167
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:10,800
and won't see the guests.

168
00:17:11,590 --> 00:17:12,830
I'm afraid that those light blue curtains

169
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:14,950
have been there for a long time.

170
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:16,800
I think

171
