186
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,310
I'm Chang Qing, the 17th descendant

187
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,950
of the Chang family of Yangzhou,
a family that makes soup dumplings.

188
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:07,280
Now, I'm the accountant and waiter
of Tianxiang Restaurant.

189
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:09,760
Nice to meet you, Mister.

190
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:14,800
