220
00:19:15,430 --> 00:19:16,640
What's so special about the mermaid?

221
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:18,760
It's described in "Bai Ze's Supernatural Creatures"

222
00:19:18,760 --> 00:19:20,040
that this mermaid has a snake-shaped head
and a fish-shaped body.

223
00:19:20,040 --> 00:19:21,110
She also has two legs

224
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:22,560
and lives in deep cold water.

225
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:25,040
This is much more precious than bass

226
00:19:25,040 --> 00:19:26,280
and a rare delicacy too.

227
00:19:47,660 --> 00:19:51,700
[Zhu]

228
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:02,880
Too bad.

229
00:20:03,040 --> 00:20:04,520
The meat is tender and soft,

230
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:05,710
but an important taste

231
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:06,520
is missing.

232
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:10,230
How... How's that possible?

233
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:11,350
It's so fresh.

234
00:20:11,760 --> 00:20:12,310
How about you

235
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:13,760
taste it again?

236
00:20:14,110 --> 00:20:15,430
It's fresh, yes.

237
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:16,110
But

238
00:20:16,110 --> 00:20:18,040
she has been trapped in this jar

239
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:19,040
so of course she's distressed.

240
00:20:19,040 --> 00:20:20,160
And she must have been scared and sad

241
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,280
on the way here.

242
00:20:21,350 --> 00:20:22,350
Of course it won't taste good

243
00:20:22,350 --> 00:20:23,350
when the meat is bitter.

244
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:25,070
What she needs

245
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:27,800
is a special feeling.

246
00:20:28,070 --> 00:20:30,070
With this feeling,

247
00:20:30,190 --> 00:20:31,160
even if she'll be in pieces, she will still say yes.

248
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:34,760
What is that?

249
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:45,560
That is called

250
00:20:46,310 --> 00:20:46,950
love.

251
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:51,310
Help! Help!

252
00:20:51,800 --> 00:20:52,560
Help!

253
00:20:57,470 --> 00:20:58,110
Once,

254
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:01,520
I woke up on the beach
after falling into the water accidentally

255
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:04,110
and the first person I saw was her.

256
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:06,640
